{"type":null,"faqId":26105,"title":"开启 WLAN 后，如果搜不到网络，耗电量仍会比较大，为什么？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>平板 在 WLAN 搜索上默认的休眠策略是永不休眠，即如果没有可连接的 WLAN 网络，WLAN 也只是进入低功耗模式，其芯片仍在工作，所以耗电量会比较快。只有在关闭屏幕十几分钟后，WLAN芯片才会停止搜索并自动断电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.6.9.2.2\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=91061\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>建议您在 WLAN 搜索不到网络时，手动关闭 WLAN 以节约电量。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"425","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1432262701000,"seriesProductName":"T1-A21w","visitedTimes":22,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"耗电,耗电量大,搜不到网","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}